reviewText: K. Galindo is good, movie good

Bad movies were the normal in the late '80's, this one may be the worst of the worst.
If you are looking for hot chicks naked and doing anything like moving around in a dance to show off that hot body, this is a dead end.
One chick, with '80's boobs (tiny), dancing badly. Ten seconds at best. The rest is, but for some language, a made for TV, shot on video, no drama soap opera-like waste of time. Seriously, do not waste a single penny on this loser.

This is a hard to find movie and i finally have it! I Didn't think i would get it, but i finially have it! And just in case you don't know, Lawrence-Hilton Jacobs directed this movie! You have to order it on amazon just like i did! You can't get it from best buy,blockbuster,fye,you can't even get it at wal-mart! You have to find a local old video ware-house or at amazon! Gotta love this movie! The best!
Thanks Amazon!
